for creativity

218
00:11:07.560 --> 00:11:10.280
and all the different ways
you can make it look pretty

219
00:11:10.280 --> 00:11:12.000
and eye-catching and beautiful.

220
00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:16.320
My dream is to have my
own patisserie one day.

221
00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:19.240
where I can surprise people with
unique flavour combinations

222
00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:21.640
through sweets
that they already know and love.

223
00:11:22.680 --> 00:11:24.480
ANDY AND SOFIA: Hey. Bella.
Hey.

224
00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:25.840
OK. I can see you're
pretty locked in.

225
00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:27.200
so I'm gonna keep
this very short.

226
00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:28.680
