227
00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:31.400
I'm cooking a spiced apple
entremet for you guys today.

228
00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:33.680
It's a birthday cake
I like to make my family.

229
00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:36.000
