914
00:45:42.720 --> 00:45:43.720
Crazy.

915
00:45:43.720 --> 00:45:45.880
Their content is
absolutely awesome.

916
00:45:45.880 --> 00:45:49.640
And with their first
service challenge...

917
00:45:49.640 --> 00:45:51.240
(ALL CHEER)

918
00:45:51.240 --> 00:45:53.840
Never really cooked
for a lot of people before.

919
00:45:53.840 --> 00:45:57.080
.. and a surprise immunity pin
on the line...

920
00:45:57.080 --> 00:45:58.560
(CHEERING)

921
00:45:58.560 --> 00:46:01.200
.. they're absolutely clamouring

922
00:46:01.200 --> 00:46:04.320
to create something
stratospheric.

923
00:46:04.320 --> 00:46:06.400
Are we going viral here?
Yes.

924
00:46:06.400 --> 00:46:09.480
POH: I flippin' love this dish
so much.

925
00:46:09.480 --> 00:46:10.480
This is. like.

926
00:46:10.480 --> 00:46:11.960
competition-winning-worthy
stuff.

